item.description: Preface I am not sure if the preface would exist in the following posts. The reason why here’s a preface is because I decided to start jotting down my feeling and thoughts, and I hope this preface is used as a anchor expalining the beginning for everthing in the future. I was kind of lost after failing the interview with Bloomberg. It felt like all the drive and hope was disappear after all that.
